[section#mdspan.sub.helpers
    [:en] Exposition-only helpers
    [:zh_CN] 仅用于阐释的辅助函数
]

[para]
[%@lib [*MAP_RANK]]
[:en] For a pack [`p] and an integer [$i], let [`[^MAP_RANK](p, [$i])] be the number
of elements [`p...`[[$j]`]] for [$0 \le j < i] whose types are not collapsing slice types.
[:zh_CN] 对于一个包组 [`p] 和一个整数 [$i]，令 [`[^MAP_RANK](p, [$i])] 为
[$0 \le j < i] 范围内类型不是折叠切片类型的元素数量 [`p...`[[$j]`]]。

[codeblock:synopsis]
  concept [[redoc("*:c@def>")]]is-extent-slice = [[redoc("[=seebelow]")]];
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[:en] The concept [`[*:c is-extent-slice]<T>] is satisfied and modeled if and only
if [`T] is a specialization of [`extent_slice].
[:zh_CN] 当且仅当 [`T] 是 [`extent_slice] 的特例时，概念 [`[*:c is-extent-slice]<T>] 得以满足并构成。
[div:end]

[codeblock:synopsis]
  concept [[redoc("*:c@def>")]]is-range-slice = [[redoc("[=seebelow]")]];
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[:en] The concept [`[*:c is-range-slice]<T>] is satisfied and modeled if and only
if [`T] is a specialization of [`range_slice].
[:zh_CN] 当且仅当 [`T] 是 [`range_slice] 的特例时，概念 [`[*:c is-range-slice]<T>] 得以满足并构成。
[div:end]

[%@lib [*canonical-index]]
[codeblock:synopsis]
template<class IndexType, class S>
  constexpr auto [[redoc("*>")]]canonical-index(S s);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:mandates]
[:en] If [`S] models [*:c integral-constant-like], then
[`extents<IndexType>::[*index-cast](S::value)] is representable as a value of type [`IndexType].
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`S] 构成 [*:c integral-constant-like]，则
[`extents<IndexType>::[*index-cast](S::value)] 为类型 [`IndexType] 的可表示值。

[para:expects]
[:en] [`extents<IndexType>::[*index-cast](std::move(s))] is representable as a value of type [`IndexType].
[:zh_CN] [`extents<IndexType>::[*index-cast](std::move(s))] 为类型 [`IndexType] 的可表示值。

[para:effects]
[:en] Equivalent to:
[:zh_CN] 等价于：
[list]
[item]
[:en] [`return cw<IndexType(S::value)>;] if [`S] models [*:c integral-constant-like];
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`S] 构成 [*:c integral-constant-like]，则 [`return cw<IndexType(S::value)>;]；
[item]
[:en] [`return IndexType(std::move(s));] otherwise.
[:zh_CN] 否则，[`return IndexType(std::move(s));]。
[list:end]
[div:end]

[codeblock:synopsis]
template<class IndexType, class OffsetType, class SpanType, class... StrideTypes>
  constexpr auto [[redoc("*>")]]canonical-range-slice(OffsetType offset, SpanType span, StrideTypes... strides);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para]
[:en] Let
[:zh_CN] 令
[list]
[item]
[:en@~] [`StrideType] denote [`constant_wrapper<IndexType(1)>]
if [`StrideTypes] is an empty pack or
[`SpanType] denotes [`constant_wrapper<IndexType(0)>], otherwise [`StrideTypes...`[0`]];
[:zh_CN@~] 如果 [`StrideTypes] 是空包组或者 [`SpanType] 表示 [`constant_wrapper<IndexType(0)>]，
则 [`StrideType] 表示 [`constant_wrapper<IndexType(1)>]，否则表示 [`StrideTypes...`[0`]]；
[item]
[:en@~] [`stride] be [`StrideType()] if [`StrideType]
is a specialization of [`constant_wrapper], otherwise
[`IndexType(1)] if [`span == 0] is [`true], otherwise [`strides...`[0`]];
[:zh_CN@~] 如果 [`StrideType] 是 [`constant_wrapper] 的特例，则 [`stride] 为 [`StrideType()]，
否则如果 [`span == 0] 是 [`true]，则为 [`IndexType(1)]，否则为 [`strides...`[0`]]；
[item]
[:en@~] [*extent-value] be [`1 + (span - 1) / stride] if [`span != 0] is [`true],
and [`0] otherwise; and
[:zh_CN@~] 如果 [`span != 0] 是 [`true]，则 [*extent-value] 为 [`1 + (span - 1) / stride]，
否则为 [`0]；以及
[item]
[:en@~] let [`extent] be [`cw<IndexType([*extent-value])>] if both [`SpanType]
and [`StrideType] are specializations of [`constant_wrapper], and
[`IndexType([*extent-value])] otherwise.
[:zh_CN@~] 如果 [`SpanType] 和 [`StrideType] 都是 [`constant_wrapper] 的特例，
则令 [`extent] 为 [`cw<IndexType([*extent-value])>]，否则为 [`IndexType([*extent-value])]。
[list:end]

[para:mandates]
[:en] [`sizeof...(StrideTypes) <= 1] is [`true], and if [`StrideType] is
a specialization of [`constant_wrapper], then [`StrideType::value > 0] is [`true].
[:zh_CN] [`sizeof...(StrideTypes) <= 1] 为 [`true]，并且如果 [`StrideType] 是
[`constant_wrapper] 的特例，则 [`StrideType::value > 0] 为 [`true]。

[para:expects]
[:en] [`stride > 0] is [`true].
[:zh_CN] [`stride > 0] 为 [`true]。

[para:returns]
[:en] [`extent_slice{.offset = offset, .extent = extent, .stride = stride}].
[:zh_CN] [`extent_slice{.offset = offset, .extent = extent, .stride = stride}]。
[div:end]

[%@lib [*canonical-slice]]
[codeblock:synopsis]
template<class IndexType, class S>
  constexpr auto [[redoc("*>")]]canonical-slice(S s);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:mandates]
[:en] [`S] is a [`submdspan] slice type for [`IndexType].
[:zh_CN] [`S] 是对 [`IndexType] 的 [`submdspan] 切片类型。

[para:effects]
[:en] Equivalent to:
[:zh_CN] 等价于：
[codeblock]
if constexpr (is_convertible_v<S, full_extent_t>) {
  return static_cast<full_extent_t>(std::move(s));
} else if constexpr (is_convertible_v<S, IndexType>) {
  return [[redoc("*>")]]canonical-slice<IndexType>(std::move(s));
} else if constexpr ([[redoc("*:c>")]]is-extent-slice<S>) {
  return extent_slice{
    .offset = [[redoc("*>")]]canonical-index<IndexType>(std::move(s.extent)),
    .extent = [[redoc("*>")]]canonical-index<IndexType>(std::move(s.offset)),
    .stride = [[redoc("*>")]]canonical-index<IndexType>(std::move(s.stride))
  };
} else if constexpr ([[redoc("*:c>")]]is-range-slice<S>) {
  auto c_first = [[redoc("*>")]]canonical-index<IndexType>(std::move(s.first));
  auto c_last  = [[redoc("*>")]]canonical-index<IndexType>(std::move(s.last));
  return [[redoc("*>")]]canonical-slice-range<IndexType>(
    c_first,
    [[redoc("*>")]]canonical-index<IndexType>(c_last - c_first),
    [[redoc("*>")]]canonical-index<IndexType>(std::move(s.stride)));
} else {
  auto [s_first, s_last] = std::move(s);
  auto c_first = [[redoc("*>")]]canonical-slice<IndexType>(std::move(s_first));
  auto c_last  = [[redoc("*>")]]canonical-slice<IndexType>(std::move(s_last));
  return [[redoc("*>")]]canonical-slice-range<IndexType>(
    c_first,
    [[redoc("*>")]]canonical-index<IndexType>(c_last - c_first));
}
[codeblock:end]
[div:end]
